   <p xml:id="180" begin="00:05:02.420" end="00:05:06.791">IN THE CHRON CITE ERA.</p>
   <p xml:id="181" begin="00:05:04.288" end="00:05:09.860">IF HE HAD HAD DONE WHAT</p>
   <p xml:id="182" begin="00:05:06.857" end="00:05:11.996">CHARLES BLOW DID, THAT IS,</p>
