   <p xml:id="184" begin="00:05:12.063" end="00:05:15.166">CONTEXT FROM A WEB SITE,</p>
   <p xml:id="185" begin="00:05:13.998" end="00:05:17.134">DIDNT MENTION IN HIS COLUMN</p>
   <p xml:id="186" begin="00:05:15.232" end="00:05:18.736">THAT HE DID THAT, BLOW</p>
